<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Trivia_sections" title="Wikipedia:Trivia sections">Lists of miscellaneous information</a> should be avoided.</b> Please <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Handling_trivia#Recommendations_for_handling_trivia" title="Wikipedia:Handling trivia">relocate</a> any relevant information into appropriate sections or articles. <small><i>(July 2007)</i></small></td>
